item.title: RIP Pippin 2020-2026
item.description: I didn't know he could fly that well right now. I was getting groceries out of the car and accidentally hit the horn and he flew away. I cant find him. I cant hear him. There is no response. He just took off. I've been looking for an hour. Nothing. I will miss you, and thank you, Pippin, for the final lesson that everything and everyone that I love will abandon me in a heartbeat. I dont deserve nice things or love in my life and this is the final proof. Goodbye, snugglesaurus. Goodbye. EDIT: nevermind, the absolute Fool of a Took is back now, thank goodness.
